name: Singsing kelesih Waterfall
address: J4J8+6RQ, Jatiluwih, Penebel, Tabanan Regency, Bali 82152, Indonesia
review 1:
Nice waterfall including a man, which is the main attraction to the place. You can see him in the pictures. Very kind, well-spoken, and explained why the waterfall has water and falls. I didn't expect such a natural attraction close to the rice fields.

Looking forward to meet the rice field man
